== Welcome To United-Dictionary

We aim to bring the dictionary out of the hands of restricted repositories and into the masses. We want to open language translation tools and do anything else remotely interesting or helpful that can be done. This was the first website created by Richard Schneeman and needs bit of of improvement. 

Eventually it would be great if we had an ...

More Tools - 	Such as a YML translator to help with internationalization, improvement on the picture translation matching 		
			 	game and more
			
ASPELL integration - Auto generate and remotely host dictionaries to be used by ASPELL (used in search spell checking)

API - This dictionary is to bring info to the people


Anything you can think of ... Visit us at www.uniteddictionary.com and leave feedback on what you want to see added








